body.description: Equip your kitchen for less with these essential knives. The 7-piece knife block set features all the knives you need to set your kitchen up right. From the paring knife for smaller scale jobs to the chef’s knife for slicing and dicing, this set contain the key knives for all kitchen jobs, along with a sturdy set of kitchen shears. The set comes housed in a handsome, compact wood knife block. Honed for long-lasting sharpness, these fine-edge blades make fast work of kitchen prep. Since 1895, Henckels has been making high quality knives at an exceptional value. Solution knives are designed to tackle every kitchen task. Fabricated from high-quality stainless steel, the single-piece, precision-stamped knife blades are lightweight without sacrificing strength and durability. Curved for comfort, the break-proof, triple-rivet handles are pleasant to grip, giving you the control you need to slice through tougher cuts with ease. This ergonomic handle lets you enjoy maximum maneuverability and fatigue-free cutting. Set includes 4-inch Paring Knife, 5-inch Serrated Utility Knife, 6-inch Utility Knife, 8-inch Bread Knife, 8-inch Chef's Knife, Kitchen Shears and 6 slot Hardwood Block.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Big Improvement
reviews.reviewText: Our old set of kitchen knives were a wedding present from many years ago and were virtually impossible to keep sharp. This set is amazing. We had no idea how bod our old set had gotten until we replaced them. These cut wonderfully and seem to hold an edge quite well. I hone them with a Henckels sharpener I purchased separately to keep that nice edge. These are well worth the price to make kitchen work much easier and more enjoyable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Gift for Family
reviews.reviewText: Gift for family member who loved the knives.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great knife assortment
reviews.reviewText: This is exactly what I needed. I already have steak knives so this block of knives works well. I have bought Henkels before so I am very happy with this purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Average, does the job but not sturdy at all
reviews.reviewText: These knives are sharp but not sturdy at all which makes them kind of dangerous in my opinion. I would not recommend this for beginners, they are good for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My own set
reviews.reviewText: I purchased these so only I can use them, and they are great totally worth the buy

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Seem a bit light
reviews.reviewText: We've had Henckles knives before. These seem a bit light as far as weight goes. Previous ones had heft to them, not these. Almost feel a little cheap. Not a bad value for the money though.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars They are sharp!
reviews.reviewText: These are sharp knives. If you have not owned chef knives, keep your head out of your grommet or you will be missing a few digits!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 16, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Frustrated with knives that don't deliver, try Henkels. Sharp upon arrival and perform as you would expect a knife to.
These are supposedly made of stainless steel, but within a month of purchase they began to rust already.
Easy to hold and reasonably priced.
